    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "NORTHWEST\nAIRLINES\nSome People Just Know How To Fly.\nFlight\nSchedule\nEffective\nDec. 19,\n1997\nFor\nNonstop\nand Direct\nFlights\nBRIDGING\nthe PACIFIC\nKLM\nNORTHWEST\nGRAND CAYMAN",
      "NORTHWEST\nWolVeratine: Gold\nLuxurious vacations at a value price.\nExclusive Vacation Packages\nfrom Northwest Airlines\nWelcome to Northwest WorldVacations Gold. We\noffer luxury vacation packages exclusively from\nNorthwest Airlines to Hawaii including the islands\nof Oahu, Hawaii, Kauai, Lanai, Maui, and Molokai.\nThe WorldVacations Gold Difference\nV Discounted First-Class Airfares\nV Luxurious Accommodations\nExceptional Add-Ons\nV Luxury Car Rentals\nV Personalized Service\n2,000 WorldPerks® Bonus Offer\nPurchase a WorldVacations Gold package between Dec 2, 1997\nand Feb 28, 1998 and you'll receive an extra 2,000 WorldPerks\nBonus Miles. That's in addition to actual miles flown and the 500\nWorldVacations WorldPerks Bonus Miles you receive when\npurchasing an air and hotel package to Hawaii.\nCall your travel agent or\nORLDW,\nKLM\nWorldVacations Gold at 1-800-990-0058.\n©1997 Northwest Airlines Inc.\nWVMS5326"
    ],
